{"tid":2330070,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"赤柱田灣懲教署職員宿舍：3歲男童確診，正住院","createTime":"2020-12-17T16:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T16:53:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5bde7c7dddb481c174d84177ad0dd401f34c0883","tid":2330070,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:46:39.000Z","msg":"個案 7105: 男 3歲  香港居民<br />\n住院/出院/死亡: 住院 <br />\n09/12/2020 (確診)<br />\n07/12/2020 (發病)<br />\n與本地個案有流行病學關連<br />\n <br />\n居住過/到訪過的大廈: <br />\n南區 田灣懲教署職員宿舍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202012/09/P2020120900805_356193_1_1607524450131.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F09%2FP2020120900805_356193_1_1607524450131.pdf&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=848cb95e\" target=\"_blank\">https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202012/09/P2020120900805_356193_1_1607524450131.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"27a6bb64b15e211e8c661107ce2db8c9ea3ad027","tid":2330070,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:53:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2061750/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2061750/page/1</a><br />\n[藍絲懲教殺人早有前科]2002年小欖精神病治療中心曾用毒藥殺囚<br />\n<br />\n1)立會聲稱：有意投訴也會被打針<br />\n三釋囚爆懵仔針黑幕<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20021106/2929931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20021106%2F2929931&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=951cddf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20021106%2F2929931&h=3ed296cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20021106/2929931</a><br />\n<br />\n2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr02-03/chinese/panels/se/papers/se0123cb2-947-01-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr02-03%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fse%2Fpapers%2Fse0123cb2-947-01-c.pdf&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=72bf3c6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr02-03/chinese/panels/se/papers/se0123cb2-947-01-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1)囚犯張志堅被注射過量「懵仔針」致死事件<br />\n死者張志堅因得罪精神病治療中心館方<span class=\"xx-large\">遭注射過量藥處死</span><br />\n而唔少曾嘗試投訴或得罪管方的人都曾遭捉去打「懵仔針」<br />\n<br />\n2)故意用高量藥物<ins>殺人立威</ins>,令囚犯係死亡威脅下聽話係香港懲教一直的手法<br />\n大家查下定時定侯就有一批囚犯離奇死亡/重傷,<ins>明顯有計劃有組織的</ins><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">最後就只有幾頁無撚聊的立法會文書, 殺人者不受追責</span>"}]}